==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Passenger mile
<hw>Pas"sen*ger mile</hw>. <fld>(Railroads)</fld> <def>A unit of
measurement of the passenger transportation performed by a railroad
during a given period, usually a year, the total of which consists of
the sum of the miles traversed by all the passengers on the road in the
period in question.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Passenger mileage</ent>⟦br⟧
